Name: Hentai Cyberpunk
About the game: Hentai Cyberpunk is a Third Person Shooter Game, Wave Based. Fight to survive the waves of enemies falling on you with their own abilities, also formidable Bosses. Fight against robotic enemies ! Different AIs to challenge you, all differents; unique ! 5 camera angles to have fun (Always there ;) ) Futuristic Firearms (Assault Rifle, Shotgun, Sniper, Rocket Launcher) Glute and Breast Physic ! Amazing Maps in a far distant future ! Futuristic Sci-Fi theme
